&lt;h3&gt;Other Interesting Papers:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.open-std.org/jtc1/sc22/wg21/docs/papers/2022/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;2022&lt;/a&gt; /
